GuideContent.title: The Baby In Yellow
GuideContent.description: The Baby In Yellow is a prominent name in the current mobile game chart. In the game, you will play the role of a baby sister and take care of a child for a few days when the childâ€™s parents are away.

GuideContent.title: Step 1
GuideContent.description: Download the game and start it up, select Press Here To Start to enter the game.

GuideContent.title: Step 2
GuideContent.description: After entering the game, when approaching the baby, the door, the refrigerator and some other items, you will see a hint icon appear as shown below.

GuideContent.title: Step 3
GuideContent.description: The simple tasks are to get milk to change diapers and put the baby to sleep, if you need milk, go to the room at the bottom of the stairs. Open the refrigerator and you will see milk.
